Product name: Timbrefone™ Strata Walnut - Phone Amplifier // Acoustic Wood Speaker // iPhone amp // Passive Speaker
Description:
Timbrefone is a unique, handcrafted acoustic wood amplifier for your phone.
Once nestled in the unique cradle—sound produced by your phone’s speaker is focused into the unique acoustic cone, significantly amplifying the sound naturally. No cords, batteries or additional power required. The cradle comfortably fits all iPhones along with most phone cases.  The warm, full tone created by your phone through the Timbrefone is nothing short of amazing.
Great for around the house, office, patio or anywhere you want to enjoy your music without needing to plug-in. Timbrefone also works great for FaceTime, Skype or conference calls.
The Timbrefone Strata is handcrafted from Baltic Birch and a layer of Walnut for a unique band of added beauty. It is then hand finished with Danish Oil.
REVIEW BY AUDIO PRO: Sound & Vision Magazine //
http://www.soundandvision.com/content/review-timbrefone#O8kZW3O6qyuhJtmd.97
MADE IN THE USA
Dimensions: 
7 ½” x 5 ½” x 3”  
Fits: 
All iPhone models with extra room to accommodate most phone cases. Fits other phones of similar size with speaker located on bottom / right. Cradle Size: 3/4"H x 3-3/8"W x 3/4"D
Care: 
Treat the Timbrefone like your phone (ie. don’t leave it in very wet locations). If it gets dirty, simply wipe it with a damp cloth.
HOW WE GIVE BACK: 
To reduce our impact on the environment one tree is planted for every Timbrefone we sell.
